<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich VI. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Wirich von Treuchtlingen am nächsten Sonntag an einem Schiedsgericht zu Würzburg teilnimmt; danach kann er zu Burggraf Friedrich kommen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_404" id="201v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_404_r1l1"><expan>Burgg<ex>ra</ex>f</expan> <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_404_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / . Als wir 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvirichs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Trewtlingen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l3">yecʒunden 
<del rend="strikethrough">gar no </del> auf einen tag cʒü <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf den <expan>nehſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l4">Suntag / gar <expan>notlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bedürffen wan vvir ſüſt <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l5">alſpalde <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> /. vnd Jn <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l6">darauf cʒe reiten / . Alſo hat er mit vns geredt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_404_line_1576479938183_509">wie Jr ſein </ab><ab facs="#facs_404_line_1576479941583_514">auch 
<del rend="strikethrough">bed </del> auf </ab><ab facs="#facs_404_line_1576479943898_519"><expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag </ab><ab facs="#facs_404_line_1576479946312_524">bedörfft vnd </ab></add> / daʒ vvir Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l10"><expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von dem 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_404_r1l8"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒe <expan>reıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l12">das vvir auch getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllen / . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l14">heten auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> gegünnet / <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l15">vvir ſein ſelber <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Jſt es nu daʒ Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l17">alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wil / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Das </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_404_line_1589901152882_480">So </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbt</expan> Jm gen <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_404_r1l16">auf den <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Sunt<ex>ag</ex></expan> </ab></add> / vvohın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_404_r1l19">er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_404_r1l18">fürbas </ab></add> cʒü <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kumen ſülle / vnd wo etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_404" id="201v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
