<ab><expan>Burgg<ex>ra</ex>f</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als wir <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wirichs
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Trewtlingen yeczunden auf einen tag czü
                        <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                            <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> suntag</q>In Frage kommen 24./31.01./07./14./21.02.1412</note></app> gar
                            <expan>notlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bedürffen, wan wir süst
                                <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> alspalde
                            <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und in <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darauf
                        cze reiten, also hat er mit uns geredt, <add>wie ir sein auch auf
                                    <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag bedörfft und</add> daz wir im
                                <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, von dem tag <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></add> czu
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cze <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das wir
                        auch getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllen; und heten auch
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> gegünnet, <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        sein selber <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Ist es nu, daz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnade also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wil, <add>so</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan> im gen <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<add>auf den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>sunt<ex>ag</ex></expan></add>, wohin er
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>fürbas</add> czü <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kumen sülle. Und wo etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
